\f0\fs24 \cf0 How To Write Resume in English
\f1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sl300\sa360\ql\qnatural

\f0\fs20 \cf0 Writing a resume in English can be very different than in your native tongue. The following how to outlines a standard resume format.
\f1\fs24 \

\f0\fs20 Difficulty Level: Hard \'ca\'ca\'ca\'ca Time Required: 2 hours
\f1\fs24 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl360\sa320\ql\qnatural
\cf0 \
